<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>If a bootstrap resource needs  a reference to another resource, one would need to call {{$this-&gt;bootstrap('resource')}} first then {{$res = $this-&gt;getResource('resource')}}, or chain them like {{$res = $this-&gt;bootstrap('resource')-&gt;getResource('resource')}}. It would be nice if they can be combined in a single call. E.g.</p>

<p>{{$this-&gt;bootstrap('frontController')-&gt;registerPlugin(new My_Plugin());}}</p>

<p>{{list($view, $layout, $modules) = $this-&gt;bootstrap(array('view', 'layout', 'modules'));}}</p>

